The test checks a Union with certain children. But the new rule will remove unnecessary Union.

So the check

```
// After optimizer, four 'union.deduplicate' operations should be assert(unionDF.queryExecution.optimizedPlan.collect {
  case u: Union if u.children.size == 5 => u
}.size === 1)
```

will fail.

